Installation procedure for calix
================================

Calix is an Finite Element solver for 2D and 3D elasticity, thermodynamics and
thermo-elasticity. pyFormex uses it for some examples.

The install procedure will download, compile and install calix.

By default the installation is done under /usr/local and you will need root
privileges to do so.

The full installation can be done with a single command (as root):
./install.sh all


